<h2>About Me</h2>
<div class='widget-content'>
<a href='http://www.blogger.com/profile/05853899131970655876'><img alt='My Photo' class='profile-img' height='80' src='http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_vw9l2nnub6c/SbdPsr4-eBI/AAAAAAAAADY/MACANXS3zv0/S220/dgreen2.jpg' width='67'/></a>
<dl class='profile-datablock'>
<dt class='profile-data'>David Green</dt>
<dd class='profile-textblock'>I'm VP of Engineering at <a href="http://tasktop.com">Tasktop Technologies</a>,  improving the effectiveness of developers worldwide via Tasktop's revolutionary task-focused interface, built on the Eclipse Mylyn open source framework.</dd>
</dl>
